{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10034445\charrsid14965953 Okay.  Well, I decide to go to the village, to Cyprus.  I\rquote ve got the name of the village.  I suppose I got some kind 
of a map of Cyprus.  I\rquote m not quite sure how I\rquote m going to get to the village, but it\rquote s doable my father says \endash  there\rquote s roads, there\rquote s cars, there\rquote s busses.  So okay, I got the name of the village.  He
\rquote s written to some of my cousins, so I go on a boat - you get on a train in London, and it }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid6226561\charrsid14965953 goes all the way down to Bari.  }{\rtlch\fcs1 
