\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid8202754\charrsid14965953 h he was writing a book about.  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10034445\charrsid14965953 Who else?   None o
