Yes.  Well, just the last question, which is quite simple. The book\rquote s title, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \i\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10034445\charrsid14965953 The Greek Gift}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10034445\charrsid14965953 , that\rquote s a beautiful title, but I just wondered what it actually means.
